## HUD METRICS (OFF-CONTROLLER LOGIC)

* Financial Audit Ticker: Debt tracking is completely removed from the controller mapping. Active lifetime debt, interest accumulation, and structural damage penalty fees are displayed live on the HUD ticker as an inverse score mechanic
